<p class="basictext">
<b>Important:&nbsp;&nbsp;</b>
<br>
Ryerson full-time undergraduate students must obtain Career Boost approval from Student Financial Assistance (SFA) prior to applying for any jobs listed below. If you have any questions about this approval process, please visit the SFA website <a href="http://www.ryerson.ca/sfa/student_employment.html">http://www.ryerson.ca/sfa/student_employment.html</a> or directly email <a href="mailto:jobs@ryerson.ca">jobs@ryerson.ca</a>.
</p>

<p class="basictext">
The deadline to apply for Fall/Winter Career Boost approval is Friday, January 22, 2021.
</p>

<p class="basictext">
<b>Student Eligibility:&nbsp;&nbsp;</b>
<br>

Only Ryerson full-time undergraduate students who have received confirmation of Career Boost approval from Student Financial Assistance are eligible. Graduate students and students who are graduating this year are not eligible for this program.
<br>

<br>
</p>
<p class="basictext">

	<b>Program Details:</b>
	<ul class="basictext">
	
	<li><b>Employment Period:</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Fall Term: September 14 to December 11, 2020; Winter Term: January 11 to April 9, 2021</li>



	<li><b>Number of Hours:</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Up to 98 hours per term. No more than 15 hours per week. No overtime permitted.</li>
	<li><b>Number of weeks:</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Up to 13 weeks per term.</li>
	

	<li><b>Hourly Wage:</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$18.85/hour (+ 4% vacation + 8.75% benefits)</li>
	</ul>
	
</p>
